## S3-T05: API Lambda Handler — REST CRUD Endpoints

**Completed:** 2026-04-05

### Deliverables

1. **`cmd/api/main.go`** — Full Lambda entry point with init()-time initialization of DynamoDB, Redis, rate limiter, code generator, and URL validator. Chi router with generated handler registration. Supports LOCAL_MODE for development and Lambda execution for production.

2. **`cmd/api/server.go`** — `APIServer` struct implementing the full generated `ServerInterface`:
   - `POST /api/v1/shorten` — guest creation with rate limiting, 24h TTL, cache warming
   - `POST /api/v1/links` — authenticated creation with custom alias support
   - `GET /api/v1/links` — paginated list by owner
   - `GET /api/v1/links/{code}` — get link with ownership check
   - `PATCH /api/v1/links/{code}` — partial update with cache invalidation
   - `DELETE /api/v1/links/{code}` — soft-delete with cache invalidation
   - `GET /api/v1/me` — placeholder user profile
   - Stats endpoints — stubs returning empty data (Sprint 5)
   - Redirect/password endpoints — delegate to redirect Lambda (501)

3. **`cmd/api/server_test.go`** — 10 handler tests via httptest:
   - GuestShorten 201, GuestShorten rate-limited 429
   - CreateLink 201, CreateLink invalid URL 400, CreateLink duplicate alias 409
   - ListLinks 200, GetLink 200, GetLink not found 404
   - UpdateLink 200, DeleteLink 204

4. **`pkg/apierr/errors.go`** — Added `WriteJSON` and `WriteProblem` helpers

